Take evasive action!

241
00:19:40,280 --> 00:19:43,390
Luffy, hard aport!

242
00:19:43,390 --> 00:19:45,410
Yeah, I got it!

243
00:19:45,410 --> 00:19:49,500
No! You have to say "steady"
at times like this!

244
00:19:49,500 --> 00:19:50,880
Oh, that's right.

245
00:19:51,370 --> 00:19:54,130
Luffy, hard aport!

246
00:19:54,130 --> 00:19:57,340
Hard aport! Steady!

247
00:20:01,380 --> 00:20:03,430
Let's fight hand-to-hand! Lay aboard!

248
00:20:05,850 --> 00:20:08,220
Wait for them to come aboard!

249
00:20:08,220 --> 00:20:09,550
I got it!

250
00:20:09,550 --> 00:20:11,480
Don't cry, Luffy!

251
00:20:11,480 --> 00:20:12,580
Okay!

252
00:20:24,790 --> 00:20:26,670
We won!

253
00:20:26,670 --> 00:20:28,240
Yeah!

254
00:20:28,240 --> 00:20:30,040
That'll teach you!

255
00:20:33,960 --> 00:20:35,420
This is nice!

256
00:20:35,420 --> 00:20:37,200
Yeah, it's great!

257
00:20:38,610 --> 00:20:41,340
This is our hideout!

258
00:20:41,860 --> 00:20:43,510
Here they are!

259
00:20:44,440 --> 00:20:47,720
--Can't you find them yet?!
--I'm sorry!

260
00:20:47,720 --> 00:20:51,800
We talked to people who saw them at
the Gray Terminal or in the jungle

261
00:20:51,800 --> 00:20:53,730
but we couldn't find them!

262
00:20:53,730 --> 00:20:56,270
It's been 2 weeks!

263
00:20:56,270 --> 00:21:00,320
Maybe they were eaten by the
big tiger in the jungle!

264
00:21:00,320 --> 00:21:03,190
--Boss!
--W-We found them!

265
00:21:03,190 --> 00:21:04,530
Really?!

266
00:21:04,530 --> 00:21:08,450
They built a hideout in the
huge tree deep in the jungle!

267
00:21:08,450 --> 00:21:11,160
We can take you there!

268
00:21:11,160 --> 00:21:12,450
I see!

269
00:21:12,450 --> 00:21:17,060
--I'm happy for you, boss!
--You were worrying so much!

270
00:21:17,060 --> 00:21:20,740
Oh crap! Are they still alive?

271
00:21:20,740 --> 00:21:23,380
I can't believe that those
brats are so tenacious!

272
00:21:24,510 --> 00:21:26,510
W-What?

273
00:21:26,510 --> 00:21:31,470
Don't just stand around, guys!
Go get something for dinner!

274
00:21:31,470 --> 00:21:33,180
Yes, ma'am!

275
00:21:48,030 --> 00:21:51,780
Ace... Sabo... Wait for me...

276
00:21:52,460 --> 00:21:56,520
When they're sleeping, they
look like ordinary kids.

277
00:21:57,540 --> 00:22:00,380
Oh no, don't catch cold.

278
00:22:48,340 --> 00:22:50,010
A trap just went off!

279
00:22:51,330 --> 00:22:53,060
Someone tried to invade already?!

280
00:22:54,560 --> 00:22:57,240
Oh? Maybe it was just a glitch.

281
00:22:57,240 --> 00:23:01,480
Well, we made it in hurry so it could happen.

282
00:23:03,360 --> 00:23:04,690
Ace...

283
00:23:04,690 --> 00:23:06,150
Ouch...

284
00:23:06,550 --> 00:23:08,160
Damn!

285
00:23:08,160 --> 00:23:12,370
I'll never worry about them again!!

286
00:23:25,450 --> 00:23:30,300
When the boys are attacked by a huge
bear, a certain old man saves them.

287
00:23:30,300 --> 00:23:31,950
The man tells them

288
00:23:31,950 --> 00:23:34,640
that he once fought Gold Roger.

289
00:23:34,640 --> 00:23:37,160
Luffy is thrilled to hear a story

290
00:23:37,160 --> 00:23:40,270
about the Pirate King that
he's never heard before!

291
00:23:40,270 --> 00:23:41,730
On the next episode of One Piece!

292
00:23:41,730 --> 00:23:44,980
"Luffy Becoming an Apprentice?! A Man Who
Fought Against the King of the Pirates!"

293
00:23:44,980 --> 00:23:47,150
I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!
